	text: `Even though she has pretty much every single problem that it is possible for a dog to have... plus some new problems that she invented all by herself... she is our dog. And because she is our dog, we can pick out the tiny, almost imperceptible good qualities from the ocean of terrible qualities, and we can cling to them. Because we want to love our dog.`,
