	source: ``,
	text: `I think we could do it if we tried, if only to say, you're mine. Sofia, know that you and I, shouldn't feel like a crime. Honey, I don't want it to fade. There's things that I know could get in the way. I don't want to say goodbye, and I think that we could do it if we tried.`,
	tags: [],
