	source: ``,
	text: `The key to success is to become a successful thinker and then act on those thoughts. That doesn't mean that all your ideas and actions will always produce the desired results. At times you will feel that success is unattainable. You may even feel like giving up. I know. I've been there.`,
	tags: [],
