	text: `Since man is a part of nature and has himself changed the environment, it is perhaps permissible that he has modified the dog to fit into his world rather than excluding it and forcing its extinction. One thing is certain - most of us find the world enriched by our furry canine friends. Whatever your lifestyle, there's a dog to suit you.`,
	tags: [],
