	source: ``,
	text: `Freedom's just another word for nothing left to lose. Nothing, don't mean nothing' hon' if it ain't free, no no. And, feeling good was easy, Lord, when he sang the blues. You know, feeling good was good enough for me. Good enough for me and my Bobby McGhee`,
	tags: [],
