	text: `Shut up. Just shut up. Homer once said you love the mine more than your own family. I stuck up for you because I didn't want to believe it. Homer has gotten a lot of help from the people in this town. They've helped him build his rockets. They've watched him fly 'em. But not you, John. You never showed up, not even once. I'm not asking you to believe in it but he's your son for God's sake, John. And I am asking you to help him. If you don't I'll leave you. I'll do whatever it takes to get away from here. I will work if that's what it takes. I'll live in a tree to get away from you. Don't think I won't.`,
	tags: [],
