	source: ``,
	text: `I don't know if we each have a destiny or if we're all just floating around accidental-like on a breeze but I, I think maybe it's both. Maybe both is happening at the same time. I miss you, Jenny. If there's anything you need I won't be far away.`,
	tags: [],
