	source: ``,
	text: `Another time when I was running along somebody had lost all his money in the T-shirt business and he wanted to put my face on a T-shirt but he couldn't draw that well and didn't have a camera. Some years later I found out that man did come up with an idea for a T-shirt and he made a lot of money off of it.`,
	tags: [],
