	source: ``,
	text: `I have a younger brother named Sam. Sam's a genius. I mean literally. As a kid he tested off the charts. The first computer I ever had he built from a kit he bought with money he earned tutoring other kids in math. He's energetic and articulate, curious and funny. A great source of pride to our parents. And there's no doubt that he'd be living a great life right now except for that he's dead.`,
	tags: [],
