	text: `Did you ever once show me any friendship? Ever ask my help in a personal problem? Include me in one of your little bull sessions? Can you imagine how it feels to walk by this tent and hear you laughing and know that I'm not welcome? Did you ever offer me a lousy cup of coffee?`,
	tags: [],
